reviewText: An eye opener to a great tradition of gift wrapping.

I bought this before my son's wedding to a young women from Japan. Her parents, who spoke no English and were in the U.S. for the first time, took notice! I am of average ability, craft wise.  I had no trouble mastering the designs that were demonstrated.

I am not a wrapper but this DVD showed me great ideas and technique for wrapping that I can do.  The instruction was step-by-step and very easy to follow. I will definitely use the wrapping technique this Christmas.
